Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:13.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:15.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:22.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:24.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魯迪烏斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:30.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不好意思  請問你是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,就如你所見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:38.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,看不太清
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:41.68,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我是人神  是神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:45.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,人神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:46.77,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我一直在看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:50.28,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這不是度過了很有趣的人生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:54.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,偷窺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:55.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,對  因為很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:56.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以我一直注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:00:59.62,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我覺得你正感到為難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:02.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我是你的同伴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:04.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:05.92,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:08.25,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,讓我做異世界轉生之類的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:10.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,結果還是Game Over了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:12.71,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,看著我這麼快活很開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:14.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,完全無法相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,真困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:19.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,總而言之我先給你個建議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:19.97,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,就是有你這種人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:21.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,前世的時候也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:24.06,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,說著給建議來誘惑我的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:28.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,只要有心就總有辦法做到的年紀早就過了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:30.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,就算變得積極
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:32.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,最後都只會變成加倍的絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:33.90,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,就像現在這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:38.57,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不要誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:41.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我不是在說前世的事  是在說現在的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.54,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那我這個樣子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:47.17,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是你的精神體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:48.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,肉體沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.42,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那等我醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:54.01,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不會回到這副像屎一樣的身體是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:55.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:58.05,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,等你醒了  你的身體也會恢復原來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊  是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:04.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.64,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我也很驚訝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:09.81,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,精神體和肉體居然有這麼大差別
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:12.86,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以  你說要我做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.48,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我是異物很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:16.40,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以要我回原來的世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:17.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:20.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在這六面世界之外的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,即便是我也沒法把人送回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:27.87,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,也就是說  讓我轉生到這個世界的不是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:28.92,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,算是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:32.38,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這種事是邪惡的龍神擅長做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:34.67,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,邪惡的龍神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.42,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以要聽嗎  我的建議
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:37.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不聽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:39.63,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:40.51,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:42.47,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,只聽最開始的這次就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:45.89,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.89,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這種像「只放前端進去就好了」的講法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:49.81,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,絕對是騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:51.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:56.03,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,雖說這樣下去的話  你會死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:58.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,會死？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:00.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔大陸是個非常嚴酷的大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,幾乎沒什麼吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.66,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,還有很多魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你能挺過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:11.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,等一下  那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:12.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:16.63,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,被捲入到大規模的魔力災害中  被轉移了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:20.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔力災害  是指那束光嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:23.43,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.51,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在未知的危險土地上活下去的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,知道了  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.98,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不管是建議還是什麼都好隨便你說不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.23,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:39.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:41.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魯迪烏斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:43.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:48.24,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你醒來之後  附近會有個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.62,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,依靠那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:57.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,並且幫助他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:36.71,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,基列奴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:52.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,基列奴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,斯佩路德族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:23.97,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.18,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:32.56,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,是神的使者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.27,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,雖然我不知道你的提問是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:41.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你們是從天上掉下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,人族的孩子很孱弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:47.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以生了篝火給你們暖身子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.16,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,你救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.37,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你救了我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.16,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:58.58,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,話說  這附近還有另外一名獸人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.63,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我只發現你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.34,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.26,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你看見我不害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.85,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,對救了自己的人感到害怕是很失禮的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:19.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你真是個不可思議的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我是魯迪烏斯·格雷拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,瑞傑路德·斯佩路迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.50,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,請讓我坐在旁邊  失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.50,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那個  這裡是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.43,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔大陸的東北  比耶寇亞地區
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:55.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,到了相當遙遠的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:01.52,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,從這裡回到中央大陸要費多長時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你們怎麼會出現在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:09.32,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這大概是被捲入到大規模的魔力災害中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:11.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我一定會送你們回故鄉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:27.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,放任不管的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.01,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,有損斯佩路德族的尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:34.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,雖然這份尊嚴早已滿身瘡痍了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.64,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,艾莉絲  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:42.40,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:45.23,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,斯…斯佩路德…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.69,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是斯佩路德族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,基列奴  基列奴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:54.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼不過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:56.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,對不起  魯迪烏斯  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.45,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,把你撞飛了對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:01.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,沒有遵守約定對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:01.83,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,對不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.17,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那才是正常的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.05,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我的反應是很異常的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:12.51,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,很異常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:14.80,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.01,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,並不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:26.81,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,初次…見面…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:32.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我是艾莉絲·伯…伯雷亞斯·格雷拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:35.57,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,艾莉絲·伯伯伯雷亞斯·格雷拉特嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:38.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不對  是伯雷亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:40.29,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,只是稍微結巴了下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:44.75,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我是瑞傑路德·斯佩路迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:54.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,只要能溝通  大家就能成為朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,母親大人根本就是騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:02.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,還說不早點睡的話  斯佩路德族就會來吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:05.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你就縮蜷起來裝睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,別當我是傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.69,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,向瑞傑路德先生拜託的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我們或許就能成為朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:13.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.16,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我也拜託瑞傑路德先生您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:19.45,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:22.12,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,艾莉絲  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:28.58,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,沒辦法  我就做你的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:30.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在夜裡兩個人關係變得要好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:36.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,即便不再害怕的艾莉絲說了失禮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:38.80,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,瑞傑路德非常爽快沒有在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.05,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是哪個傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:43.06,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,傳播斯佩路德族易怒的謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:45.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,突然來到未知的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這之後會是長途旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,必須把艾莉絲平安送回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:13.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,冒險開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我說過絕對不要動了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:17.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼沒看見卻知道有魔物在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:20.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,多虧了額頭上的眼睛  我能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:21.57,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,真方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:25.03,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我不止一次想過沒有這種東西就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.29,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那不如給我吧  把它挖出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.87,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.50,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是在開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:34.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,要是有把劍的話  我也能戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:37.71,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我也能用魔法幫點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.42,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,小孩子不用操多餘的心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.97,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你就待在哥哥身邊  讓他保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.26,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,誰是我哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.68,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我才是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.81,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.06,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,可憐的瑞傑路德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:56.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.32,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.11,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.32,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,不能讓他們進村子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.62,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,難道你要對小孩見死不救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:08.74,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,洛因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.79,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,他們是災害的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.54,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,才被扔到這個地方而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:15.00,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,喂  他們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,說我們很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:18.21,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以不讓我們進村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.05,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:21.97,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,洛因…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:23.93,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,他們去通知村長了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:30.43,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,商量一下應該就可以進村吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:41.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:42.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那是心靈感應
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.86,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,米格路德族即使相隔很遠也能對話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.70,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,米格路德族…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.79,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,村長  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.83,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,就是這兩個小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.17,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:56.67,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,我是魯迪烏斯·格雷拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.59,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,好有禮貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,幸好學過魔神語
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我是村長洛克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:08.35,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這個項鍊是在哪得到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.51,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,他懂人類語的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.52,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是師傅給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,哦  師傅？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:16.77,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,名字是洛琪希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:18.02,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,洛琪希！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.36,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.82,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.11,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,洛琪希是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.11,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,洛琪希是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.83,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,我女兒的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:35.16,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這裡是洛琪希的老家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:44.92,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魯迪烏斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,有個奇怪的東西在保護田地呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.26,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.31,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,仔細一看才發現這是龜殼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.23,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,一個洛琪希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:57.35,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,兩個洛琪希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.77,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,三個洛琪希  四個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:03.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,冷靜  我的神是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:05.36,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,洛琪希她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.95,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,自從女兒她離開村子以後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:10.07,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,已經有20年毫無音訊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,20年也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.66,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,米格路德族的壽命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:15.91,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,一般是多少歲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.92,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,沒出什麼意外的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.42,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,一般能活200年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:22.34,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,算起來今年她也已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.96,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,44…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:29.01,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,總而言之  洛琪希她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.14,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.56,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,現在她在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:34.89,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,根據書信所述
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:36.60,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,在西隆王國…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:37.68,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,一切安好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.90,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,是的…應該吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.15,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.28,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,平安就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:47.15,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:48.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,岳父…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:56.70,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,要是保羅他們知道我沒事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:00.83,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.29,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我們也在昨天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:06.34,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,看見流星飛往各地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,注意到了這一異常現象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:15.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這可如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.66,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你們倆關係挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:37.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:42.04,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那麼他們打算怎麼回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:44.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我會跟著他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:45.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不會只讓他們兩個人回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.55,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你跟著他們  打算怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:53.80,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那還用說  由我來保護他們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.93,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,護送他們平安回到家鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:58.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,汝無法進城的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:01.27,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不能進城嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:04.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,如果出了什麼事情  我會救他們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:09.86,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,即使把那裡的人們都殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:14.11,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,還是以和以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.91,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,只要一扯上孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.33,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你就變得什麼都不管不顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:22.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你是在10年前救下她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是你這樣亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.55,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,究竟能否夠達成你的目標呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:36.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,請問…是指什麼目標
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,瑞傑路德閣下的目標是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:45.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,希望洗刷掉斯佩路德族的惡名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:50.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這好像…不大可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:52.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,洛琪希也忠告過我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:54.57,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,對於斯佩路德族的恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:57.03,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,估計在這個世界上已經深入人心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,連艾莉絲都如此恐懼的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是斯佩路德族在戰爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:05.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,殺人不分敵我的事情是事實吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:06.83,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.34,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:13.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那是拉普拉斯的陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:19.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,拉普拉斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:22.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那傢伙背叛了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:26.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,能細說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:31.48,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:36.24,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,瑞傑路德講述了歷史的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.07,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,長槍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:41.91,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在戰爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,他賞賜了長槍給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,長槍是斯佩路德族的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:53.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,當時也有人無法捨棄靈魂使用別的長槍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:57.26,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,距今400年前的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,統一魔族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:02.31,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,從人族那裡贏得權力的英雄拉普拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:05.35,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,作為其屬下一起戰鬥的斯佩路德族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:10.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,瑞傑路德他們最終還是接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.77,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,拉普拉斯賞賜的榮譽之槍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.03,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那支長槍非常強力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.90,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,以至於讓人覺得無人能敵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:20.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是此時異變發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:25.25,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我們不知從何時起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.54,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,開始不分敵我地去襲擊周圍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:32.54,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是誰都沒有覺得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.38,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,誰都沒有發現到這個變化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:42.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我們殺光了眼前的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:45.06,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,然後在最後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.23,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,弒父弒母
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.52,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,弒妻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:51.77,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,弒兄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:54.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,刺死了自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.24,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這支長槍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是兒子為了將我從詛咒中解救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:07.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,用命換來的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:11.00,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,斯佩路德族的惡名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:13.34,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是因為我們輕易地相信了拉普拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:16.17,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,接受了詛咒之槍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:18.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是給予我們的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:22.26,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以作為戰士長的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:25.18,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,必須由我來洗清罪名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,400年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:36.57,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,他一直都是孤身一人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.86,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,一直都很懊悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:41.11,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,一直都很無力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.54,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,後悔…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:54.25,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:57.63,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,要是有身為人族小孩的我幫忙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:19:59.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,可能會帶來一些變化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我會幫助你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:05.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.39,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我會盡力而為去幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:13.90,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:22.40,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.03,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.16,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,這位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.24,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,我妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.08,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,我叫洛嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.87,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,師傅的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.16,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,太太好年輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.87,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:35.54,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,我今年可是102歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:37.38,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,非…非常年輕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.96,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,要是見到洛琪希了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.26,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,跟她說偶爾回來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.51,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:42.97,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,岳父
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.97,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,可以讓我這樣稱呼您嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:46.68,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:47.93,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:49.35,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,不開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.77,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,方便的話請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.27,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,這個也請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:55.56,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,作為告訴我們洛琪希平安消息的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.56,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:00.19,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:08.16,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,非常感謝你們的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.99,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:24.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我約定好了要幫助瑞傑路德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:29.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,生前的我就算是聽過那些話以後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.93,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,應該也會嗤之以鼻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:33.52,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是昨晚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:35.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我決定去相信他了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:39.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那時的那些話很輕易地就感動了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在城外他保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:44.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在城內我幫助他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:46.32,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這是互相幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:51.58,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,瑞傑路德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.04,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,今後也請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:55.29,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好
